8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據近日內地政府公布資料，新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情集中在武漢地區，而主要疫區都有大型海鮮市場，當中有售不少野味，而通過野生動物傳染人類的可能性較大，可能是竹鼠、獾之類，因此呼籲民眾要加倍注意，不應隨便進食。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2549011/【武漢肺炎】葉璇拍內地真人騷被逼食竹鼠%E3%80%80葉璇：不食就被責耍大牌\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2549011%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%91%89%E7%92%87%E6%8B%8D%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E9%A8%B7%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E9%A3%9F%E7%AB%B9%E9%BC%A0%25E3%2580%2580%E8%91%89%E7%92%87%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E9%A3%9F%E5%B0%B1%E8%A2%AB%E8%B2%AC%E8%80%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%8C&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=19127595\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2549011/【武漢肺炎】葉璇拍內地真人騷被逼食竹鼠%E3%80%80葉璇：不食就被責耍大牌</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:06:33.000Z","msg":"人生苦短,埋屌啦."},{"pid":"1954b64425a1bf607200f2b00cd56766483a9850","tid":1836564,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjDuqLd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjDuqLd.jpg&h=a60f0676&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa24f1c5a666640097b65b36fe3d372a226f8d49","tid":1836564,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:07:46.000Z","msg":"比錢你拍野就預左架喇 唔係d錢咁易袋 貪你咩呀"},{"pid":"87c6d4ee2e3e892fab1db46f2f34dfa576b91114","tid":1836564,"uid":151903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"當初又無人迫你去支那發展<br />\n姣婆遇著脂粉客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e21ee40fc8c362cb1b60d585cf1b282698adfb","tid":1836564,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"賺人仔又睇唔起中國野味文化 支持中國人杯葛佢"},{"pid":"e1af99ba19de988c0b9680c3b51e07b3813d6c4b","tid":1836564,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"奶得共就預咗"},{"pid":"b905324eed8620439a585aa69c1e2157bcd49ddf","tid":1836564,"uid":151926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:42:47.000Z","msg":"我唔信佢接得呢d show會唔知要做咩囉<br />\n一集百萬人仔喎，屎都食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7b7ddd672430ecc5e28f2cc4783814a99a2c5f","tid":1836564,"uid":238369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"睇左，不食就膜大脾"}]}